name: “UpToHEN”
description:
Specially made for HEN:Use a 5: 1 ratio, exaggerating the vertical side, so that this image looks really high in HEN, maybe until someone surpasses it, it is the highest up in HEN.

To better appreciate the drawing to the fullest it is recommended to scroll on your cellphone, or click on (view on ipfs).

Finally I want to thank HEN, because it is the first place where I can upload my digital works in a proper way. I appreciate that above all the other awesome things about this platform.

Digital signature: "ToTeM"
